features_names = [col for col in df.columns if col!='label']
features_raw = df.drop('label',axis=1)

In [8]:
# 绘制各feature的频数频数直方图
import math
col_len=4
row_len=math.ceil(len(features_names)/4)
f, axes = plt.subplots(row_len , col_len ,figsize=(25, 20))
i=0
for col in features_names:
    sns.distplot(df[col],ax=axes[i//col_len, i%col_len],axlabel='%s' % col);
    i+=1
plt.show()

模型的训练框架¶

针对不同模型，提供同一种训练框架，返回不同的准确率。

In [16]:
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score

def train_predict(model, X_train,y_train,X_val,y_val):
    results={}
    model=model.fit(X_train,y_train)
    predictions_val=model.predict(X_val)
    results['model']=model.__class__.__name__
    results['acc_val']=accuracy_score(y_val,predictions_val)
    return results

初始模型结果评价¶

无初始化值的RadomForestClassifier在验证集上的准确率可以达到96.25%，而XGBClassifier可以达到97.04%,两个模型都有很好的效果； 二在测试集上的结果都是97.63%。 SVC在验证集上的准确率可以达到73.96%，测试集上是76.81%。

调参¶

使用GridSearchCV调整模型的参数

In [21]:
from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')
#调优函数
def tuning(model,test_param,X_train,y_train,cv=5):
    grid_obj = GridSearchCV(estimator=model, param_grid=test_param, scoring='accuracy', n_jobs=4, iid=False, cv=cv)
    grid_obj = grid_obj.fit(X_train,y_train)
    
    best_clf = grid_obj.best_estimator_
    predictions = (model.fit(X_train, y_train)).predict(X_val)
    best_predictions = best_clf.predict(X_val)

    print("Unoptimized score: {}, Optimized score: {}".format(accuracy_score(y_val,predictions),
                                                  accuracy_score(y_val,best_predictions)))
    print("Best Params: {}, Best Score: {}".format(grid_obj.best_params_,grid_obj.best_score_))
    return grid_obj.best_params_;

XGBoost调优¶

In [24]:
import xgboost as xgb
In [25]:
def xgb_model_cv(model, X, y, cv_folds=5, early_stopping_rounds=50, seed=0):
    xgb_param = model.get_xgb_params()
    xgtrain = xgb.DMatrix(X, label=y)
    cvresult = xgb.cv(xgb_param, xgtrain, num_boost_round=model.get_params()['n_estimators'], nfold=cv_folds,
                    metrics='auc', seed=seed, callbacks=[
            xgb.callback.print_evaluation(show_stdv=False),
            xgb.callback.early_stop(early_stopping_rounds)
       ])
    num_round_best = cvresult.shape[0] - 1
    print('Best round num: ', num_round_best)
    return num_round_best

svm_clf.fit(X_train,y_train)
test_predict = svm_clf.predict(X_test)
print('Accuracy Score(test): {}'.format(accuracy_score(y_test,test_predict)))

Accuracy Score(test): 0.9794952681388013

以上通过对SVC进行网格搜索后，得到最优参数是{'C': 1000, 'kernel': 'linear'}，训练集上最优是97.95%

模型融合¶

In [50]:
import numpy as np
from sklearn.svm import SVC
from xgboost import XGBClassifier
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier, VotingClassifier
clf1 = RandomForestClassifier(random_state=random_state,n_estimators=95,max_depth=13)
clf2 = XGBClassifier(random_state=random_state,learning_rate=learning_rate, n_estimators=num_round, max_depth=max_depth,
                      min_child_weight=min_child_weight, gamma=gamma, subsample=subsample, reg_alpha=reg_alpha,
                      reg_lambda=reg_lambda, colsample_bytree=colsample_bytree, objective='binary:logistic',
                      nthread=4, scale_pos_weight=scale_pos_weight, seed=seed)
clf3 = SVC(random_state=random_state,C=1000,kernel='linear')
In [51]:
eclf1 = VotingClassifier(estimators=[
             ('rf', clf1), ('xgb', clf2), ('svc', clf3)], voting='hard')
eclf1 = eclf1.fit(X_train, y_train)

predict_test = eclf1.predict(X_test)
print('Accuracy (test):{}'.format(accuracy_score(y_test,predict_test)))
